            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automated Communication Status&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Org Wide Sending Enabled&lt;/strong&gt;:  {!$Setup.SRLG_Automated_Comms_Settings__c.Sending_Enabled__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://saddlerock.lightning.force.com/lightning/setup/CustomSettings/page?address=%2Fsetup%2Fui%2FlistCustomSettingsData.apexp%3Fid%3Da3t&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Go to Custom Setting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: If org wide sending is not enabled, then only testing users can send automated communications provided the record has the word &quot;Test&quot; in the display name. &lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are a comms testing user&lt;/strong&gt;: {!$Permission.BRIO_Automated_Comms_Tester}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://saddlerock.lightning.force.com/lightning/setup/PermSets/0PSUJ0000002IaL/PermissionSetAssignment/home&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;View Testing Permission Assignment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note:  If you are a testing user, then you can send active automated communications even when sending off for the org.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
